  "prompt": "International Tech companies currently hiring Indian Graduates (Developers)?",
  "response": "As of 2023, many international tech companies are actively hiring Indian graduates, especially in the fields of software development, data science, and engineering. Here are some prominent companies that frequently hire Indian graduates:\n\n### **1. Google**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Cloud Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Google Careers](https://careers.google.com/)\n\n### **2. Microsoft**\n   - **Roles**: Software Development Engineer, Program Manager, Data Analyst\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Microsoft Careers](https://careers.microsoft.com/)\n\n### **3. Amazon**\n   - **Roles**: Software Development Engineer, Cloud Support Associate, Data Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Amazon Jobs](https://www.amazon.jobs/)\n\n### **4. Meta (formerly Facebook)**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Machine Learning Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Meta Careers](https://www.metacareers.com/)\n\n### **5. Apple**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, iOS Developer, Data Analyst\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Apple Careers](https://www.apple.com/careers/)\n\n### **6. IBM**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Data Scientist, Cloud Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [IBM Careers](https://www.ibm.com/careers/)\n\n### **7. Accenture**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Analyst, Cloud Consultant\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Accenture Careers](https://www.accenture.com/us-en/careers)\n\n### **8. Infosys**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Cloud Architect\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Infosys Careers](https://www.infosys.com/careers.html)\n\n### **9. TCS (Tata Consultancy Services)**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Data Analyst, Cloud Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [TCS Careers](https://www.tcs.com/careers)\n\n### **10. Wipro**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Cloud Architect\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Wipro Careers](https://careers.wipro.com/)\n\n### **11. Cognizant**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Data Analyst, Cloud Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Cognizant Careers](https://www.cognizant.com/us/en/careers)\n\n### **12. ThoughtWorks**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Data Scientist, Cloud Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [ThoughtWorks Careers](https://www.thoughtworks.com/careers)\n\n### **13. Adobe**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Product Manager\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Adobe Careers](https://www.adobe.com/careers.html)\n\n### **14. Oracle**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Cloud Engineer, Data Analyst\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Oracle Careers](https://www.oracle.com/careers/)\n\n### **15. Intel**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Hardware Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Intel Careers](https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/jobs/jobs-at-intel.html)\n\n### **16. SAP**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Data Analyst, Cloud Consultant\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [SAP Careers](https://www.sap.com/india/careers.html)\n\n### **17. Deloitte**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Analyst, Cloud Consultant\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Deloitte Careers](https://www2.deloitte.com/us/en/careers.html)\n\n### **18. Capgemini**\n   - **Roles**: Software Developer, Data Analyst, Cloud Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [Capgemini Careers](https://www.capgemini.com/careers/)\n\n### **19. NVIDIA**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Data Scientist, Machine Learning Engineer\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [NVIDIA Careers](https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/about-nvidia/careers/)\n\n### **20. VMware**\n   - **Roles**: Software Engineer, Cloud Engineer, Data Analyst\n   - **Locations**: Global (including India, US, and other countries)\n   - **Website**: [VMware Careers](https://careers.vmware.com/)\n\n### **Tips for Indian Graduates:**\n1. **Update Your LinkedIn Profile**: Ensure your LinkedIn profile is up-to-date with your skills, projects, and certifications.\n2. **Network**: Connect with alumni and professionals in your desired field.\n3. **Certifications**: Consider obtaining relevant certifications (e.g., AWS, Google Cloud, Azure) to stand out.\n4. **Portfolio**: Build a strong portfolio of projects that showcase your skills.\n5. **Prepare for Interviews**: Practice coding problems, system design, and behavioral questions.\n\nThese companies often have specific hiring drives and campus recruitment programs targeting Indian graduates, so keep an eye on their career pages and job portals like **LinkedIn**, **Naukri**, and **Indeed**.",
